    <h2>3. Bookings &amp; pricing</h2>
    <p>Placeholder. Cover booking, pricing, and payment terms.</p>
    <h2>4. User responsibilities</h2>
    <p>Placeholder. Outline expected conduct and access requirements.</p>
    <h2>5. Liability</h2>
    <p>Placeholder. State limitations of liability.</p>
